data.description: UNDER CONSTRUCTION! READY MAY, 2021! USDA 100% FINANCING AVAILABLE AREA!! A spectacular 4 bedroom and 3 full bathroom home with sweeping views - thanks to the home's open layout and boxed ceiling design in the greatroom and master bedroom! Upgraded features include: Granite Counter tops Throughout and luxury vinyl tile flooring in the living room, Formal Dining Room and guest hallways. Additional features include: brick exterior, custom wood cabinets, designer luxury vinyl tile flooring from builder's selection in kitchen and wet areas, fiberglass master shower, chamfer-corner bead, vinyl Low E tilt sash windows and sodded front and side yard with plant package. Upgraded Appliances include: stainless steel dishwasher, electric separate smooth cook top, eye level wall oven and microwave, plus a vented hood. Plantation Woods is convenient to I-10, Avalon Blvd., and downtown Milton, Florida. Buyer to verify schools, lot size, HOA dues & restrictions, taxes, etc. Call for a modified pricing quote on this model. No restrictions in Plantation Woods subdivision against home owners storing their boat, motor home or camper on their property. Photographs are of a similar model home and may show features & options not available in all models.
